rows.label: tlk45310158_01_msg0001
rows.name:
At the top of this elevator is
Alba Margen, the imperial capital.

rows.label: tlk45310158_01_msg0002
rows.name:
You can buy top quality Core Chips and
accessories there, made using cutting-
edge Superbian technology.

rows.label: tlk45310158_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Any Driver would be a fool not to
pay the place a visit at least once.

rows.label: tlk45310158_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Also, most food in the Empire is pretty
awful, but there's something called
Quoteletta that's actually worth a try.

rows.label: tlk45310158_01_msg0005
rows.name:
Stay away from this stuff they call
Kascha, though. It's a kind of gruel, but
the things they put in it are just...eurgh.
